Privacy Policy
Last updated: October 29, 2023
Currency Converter collects analytical data for the purpose of improving the user experience. Additionally, the app utilizes AdMob for advertising, which also collects data to display personalized ads.
Analytics
We collect general, non-personal analytics data to understand how our users interact with the app and to improve our service. This data is anonymized and cannot be used to identify individual users.
Advertising
We use AdMob to serve ads in our app. AdMob may collect and use information about your device and browsing behavior to personalize the advertising content you see.
User Rights
In accordance with GDPR, users have the right to access, rectify, erase, and restrict processing of their personal data. Additionally, users may modify their consent settings within the app's settings at any time.
Data Protection
We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it against unauthorized or unlawful processing and against accidental loss, destruction, or damage.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
